m a uniform prior in the space of these\nparameters, we refined our sampling by iteratively fitting a truncated\nGaussian, and sampling from those Gaussians to propose new simulations with\neach iteration. Our maximum likelihood simulation (K0559) has parameters:\n$\\sigma_{eff} = 108.3$ km/s, $f_a = 0.922$ (indicating efficient mass\ntransfer), and $f_{wind1} = 0.328$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2023 17:30:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2023 19:47:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
