ery strong,\nthey nevertheless offer hope that a more general, perhaps ultimately\n``Penrose-like'', singularity theorem may be provable in the discrete spacetime\ncase too.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Mar 2023 00:46:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
